# DESeq2 Plotting Repository

This repository contains processed DESeq2 differential expression outputs and R scripts used to generate figures.

## Repository structure

```text
data/       -> DESeq2 result tables
scripts/    -> helper plotting scripts
figures/    -> generated figures
main.R      -> main execution script
```

## Requirements

- R >= 4.3
- renv

## Setup

Clone repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/deseq2-plotting.git
```

Open R inside the repository folder and run:

```r
install.packages("renv")
renv::restore()
```

## Run

```r
source("main.R")
```

Generated figures will appear in:

```text
figures/
```